Name: Digital Expo Center
About the game: Digital Expo Center is a virtual reality technology made on the Unreal Engine 4 game engine. Project is designed for various digital exhibitions. At the moment, you can enjoy being in Expo without leaving your home. The building itself is modeled after the Baku Expo Center in Azerbaijan. And there are many virtual stands. Here you can take part in : game developers, software and web developers, 3D Artist, designers, etc. A virtual stand can be used by participants to show: video, slide show presentation, as well as animation of 3D objects.
